 and secants, Aluffi algebras. The book includes sections of exercises to help put in practice the theoretic material instead of the mere complementary additions to the theory.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Feb 2023) 0aGeometry, Algebraic. 4aAlgebraische Geometrie. 4aGraduierter Modul. 4aGraduierter Ring. 4aKommutative Algebra. 4aSchnitt ‹Mathematik›. 7aMATHEMATICS / Algebra / Abstract.2bisacsh1 aRamos, Zaqueu, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishz978311099389908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022z9783110994810oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Mathematics 2022 Englishz978311099386808iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Mathematics 2022z9783110770445oZDB-23-DMA0 cEPUBz97831106377550 cprintz978311063754040uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311064069440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110640694423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110640694/original  a978-3-11-099386-8  EBOOK PACKAGE Mathematics 2022 Englishb2022  a978-3-11-099389-9  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishb2022  aEBA_CL_MTPY  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_MTPY  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESTMALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA12STME  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA18STMEE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2022  aZDB-23-DMAb2022